{"tid":43580,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇我個肥婆fd食飯叫好多餸之後又話食唔落轉頭又走去食甜品？","createTime":"2016-12-17T15:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T15:35:35.000Z","uid":22505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb67e07b361afc76208b48a0bed8887feea8d52e","tid":43580,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"先利申我唔係現場<br />\n個肥婆fd計埋佢有3個人<br />\n佢地去食大排檔3個人叫左5碟餸<br />\n最後食剩左兩碟餸各一半<br />\n叫佢地唔好嘥野打包又唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫個肥婆fd留聽日食又話聽日全日都要出街<br />\n叫佢留後日啦又話要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾個鍾後又轉場去食甜品<br />\n3條友叫左4樣甜品一碟腸粉一碗牛丸<br />\n同佢地講又話飽<br />\n個肥婆fd就話：｢女人有第二個胃｣<br />\n屌你如果有打包食埋岩岩d野就唔會浪費啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我理得你叫幾多野食唔識珍惜食物就唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f5909e818268068d6a2a789e7aa01fb39addfc","tid":43580,"uid":58866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"咁你唔打包？"},{"pid":"8120b06f7018cb120d7cc0cb03b5253e904c69b4","tid":43580,"uid":58866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你唔打包？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我mean話你聽個條友"}]}